{"tid":1805730,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"聽日遊行既同我入曬來 一人一張派街坊","createTime":"2019-12-31T19:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T04:40:23.000Z","uid":258597,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"faa53f1c3f75aea1012a245690b30094e8a5c8a8","tid":1805730,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:03:04.000Z","msg":"我整文宣唔叻，但都想為運動出一分力。<br />\n入面有大部分工會既FB PAGE。各位幫幫手，印出來派比身邊既人叫佢地入來like曬佢。而加好多工會都係前幾日先推出，得10幾個LIKE。快手叫佢地入曬來壯大工會。<br />\n<br />\n１月１日，維園見。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3mKFuvp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3mKFuvp.png&h=f6cec2c8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iHJV2Qq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiHJV2Qq.png&h=ceac50a1&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqPKbJM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqPKbJM.png&h=15e1c697&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQKNTW7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQKNTW7.png&h=e677a466&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q9SDgas.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9SDgas.png&h=65438fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a81ce0ec636e15b9cef33bafa6fa9fcdeb30cc60","tid":1805730,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:47:37.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"91d2dbb013855ec456c55181fd83b5529e11025f","tid":1805730,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:47:47.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"0375008112ff7b3a452da3beb69561721fba3049","tid":1805730,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:47:57.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"38c7a2c63fd4e02a8fcf8546aa945b7a1bd1a08b","tid":1805730,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:48:07.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"db21bd99c73e6b77099adba838e